  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a coastal landscape at sunset. Dramatic, dark clouds dominate the upper portion of the image, partially obscuring a vibrant orange and yellow sun. Rays of sunlight pierce through the cloud cover, illuminating the water and the distant land. Below, a calm sea stretches towards a coastline featuring islands, peninsulas, and a long bridge or causeway connecting landmasses. Silhouetted vegetation and hills occupy the foreground, creating a sense of depth. The overall effect is one of natural beauty and peacefulness, with a strong emphasis on the interplay of light and shadow.",
